    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>滚动与弹跳</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控充满弹性的绒球，征服扭曲且充满动态的关卡！精通精确的操作与快速反应，在充满惊喜障碍的赛道中疾速穿梭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/227aa08a9333622c0468faf65f78abe1.poster.avif?t=1770156744\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/227aa08a9333622c0468faf65f78abe1.webm?t=1770156744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/227aa08a9333622c0468faf65f78abe1.mp4?t=1770156744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义你的绒球</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个关卡中收集散落的金币，解锁绒球的新外观选项。收集每个世界中的所有金币，可获得特殊奖励，将你的绒球风格提升到新境界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/7c300ef54d1e33a2ff30b0c5b3ec7476.avif?t=1770156744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras_big/7c300ef54d1e33a2ff30b0c5b3ec7476.avif?t=1770156744 width=800 height=225 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>死亡只是成功道路上的小挫折</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好心理准备－《Fluff’n’Roll》并非胆小者的游戏！每个关卡都带来更艰难的地形，还有新的障碍和危险，极限考验你的技巧。每一次失败都是学习的机会。掌握每个关卡，熟悉地形，并在每一次尝试中完美提升你的绒球技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/ebc947dc907dcb98cd456961a3c45feb.poster.avif?t=1770156744\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/ebc947dc907dcb98cd456961a3c45feb.webm?t=1770156744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321020/extras/ebc947dc907dcb98cd456961a3c45feb.mp4?t=1770156744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
